    @allure.feature("User Registration")
    @allure.story("Registration Validation - Duplicate Email")
    @pytest.mark.ui
    def test_registration_duplicate_email(page: Page, home_page, random_user):
        """
        Test Case: Try to register with an already existing email.
        Validates that the system shows an appropriate error message.
        """
        with allure.step("1. Register a new user (first time) via API"):
            # Using API to create user (faster and more reliable)
            import requests
            requests.post(
                "https://api.practicesoftwaretesting.com/users/register",
                json=random_user
            )
    
        with allure.step("2. Try to register again with the same email via UI"):
            page.goto("/auth/register")
            page.wait_for_load_state("networkidle")
